    <string name="STRID_FUNC_STRS_LAUNCHER_GUIDE">Now you can easily create beautiful star trail movies. \nSimply choose themes and shoot a starry sky.</string>
    <string name="STRID_FUNC_SMOOTH_PHOTO_CUSTOM_GUIDE">Shoot with customizable settings such as aperture and shutter speed.\n[Shoot Mode]: P/A/S/M</string>
