    <string name="STRID_FUNC_STRLS_THEME_BRIGHT_NIGHT_GUIDE2">Effective for shooting from bright place such as city lights or moonlit night.\nAdjust the brightness of images by changing exposure compensation.</string>
    <string name="STRID_FUNC_STRLS_THEME_DARK_NIGHT_GUIDE2">Effective for shooting from a dark place where stars can be well seen in the sky.\nAdjust the brightness of images by changing shutter speed and ISO sensitivity.</string>
